{"tid":424831,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"出過一次街 個心已經囉囉亂","createTime":"2017-10-05T06:32:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-05T15:07:49.000Z","uid":139109,"like":3,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"f217becbf74a39d03217fcab8a9e79830e3d13a2","tid":424831,"uid":139109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T06:32:38.000Z","msg":"背景<br />\n佢大我9年 見過一次 出黎食飯睇戲<br />\n<br />\n去街個日大家都好開心，搭車個陣多人 我無位扶手 佢主動叫我捉住佢手臂 但我怕羞無捉到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  佢就輕輕捉住我隻手等我唔好跌<br />\n同佢傾計個陣又會無啦啦摸我個頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  女仔真係受呢招<br />\n佢仲帶我番屋企（番去放低啲野咋⋯唔好亂諗⋯佢屋企人都係到）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n去完街之後 我一直都想再見佢 我仲俾哂signal佢 話佢知我放假無街去 又話我今晚自己一個食  等等⋯<br />\n佢都好似無咩反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 淨係話「你啲朋友呢」咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  其實我想你約我阿 <br />\n<br />\n平日我地既語題都離不開 早晨⋯食飯未⋯忙唔忙⋯放工了⋯做緊咩⋯早抖⋯ <br />\n好似好簡單 無咩深入既話題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢覆我wtsapp都唔係密 20-30分鐘先覆 我已經算秒回佢 佢都好似成日唔睇電話咁 明明我問佢做緊咩 佢都話攤左係到無野做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實係咪我諗多左 你只係想搵一個得閒陪你傾計既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  你只係當我小妹妹？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efe046c6a543ee33dd43d64e82e5044be3b936e3","tid":424831,"uid":51701,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T06:33:45.000Z","msg":"未上床點知夾唔夾呀?"},{"pid":"fbedbfb0fb2780967e2a625fd2b0121bc6df6b50","tid":424831,"uid":3232,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T06:39:01.000Z","msg":"你只係佢網裡面既其中一條魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"797f74c97c131fc2aa38abc39be8261014546194","tid":424831,"uid":46674,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T06:41:45.000Z","msg":"一定同時釣緊幾十個"},{"pid":"701a68f7209ee17cc83b919010ea1657f205cd98","tid":424831,"uid":139109,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T06:44:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你只係佢網裡面既其中一條魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n嗚阿我都係咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  佢應該成日約人去街 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d831c0988b253f9eced53b502db7e02c21e4cbe2","tid":424831,"uid":139109,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T06:44:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一定同時釣緊幾十個</blockquote><br />\n不要再說了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bd6193f43c80e6c9b436c5b7db7107015adf20e","tid":424831,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T06:44:41.000Z","msg":"比佢屌完咪知"},{"pid":"f38ef82c99cae218270cda49f98ac22a1e957c9e","tid":424831,"uid":10687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T06:46:21.000Z","msg":"你靚唔靚大唔大波先問心"},{"pid":"990867c27a9b27165b37ae7043e3c12557e39e76","tid":424831,"uid":59753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T06:46:45.000Z","msg":"鐘意食洋腸"},{"pid":"f70b410593c000de5038754c32609b36763b5709","tid":424831,"uid":35746,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T06:47:08.000Z","msg":"岩既見完面 就好快約下一次啦"},{"pid":"f114ac895d7d52eb1ce5efcd46209a1e95fae39e","tid":424831,"uid":139109,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T06:48:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你靚唔靚大唔大波先問心</blockquote><br />\n認真 我自問樣唔太差<i